title: Entrepreneurship and Bitcoin with Jay Gould
description:
Blockware Lead Insights Analyst Will Clemente and Entrepreneur Jay Gould talk about Starting a business, macro uncertainty, interest rates, HyperBitcoinization and more for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Can now find our podcast on Spotify, Apple, and Google Podcasts as well!



Jay’s twitter: twitter.com/JayGould
